ette, sp\u00f8r hun.", "Les hele brevet p\u00e5 Maria Amelies blogg ."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|innenriks"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "8fce9f06c6da54f1b2f5bf5c825bc454c29ac840a87e47e45e6b195f350f1b46"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-05-26T23:42:09.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Les Maria Amelies brev til Jens Stoltenberg."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1379086.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/ameliehode169"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/85db9451f2d3e05ffc306deee171799e18634bbc.jpg?5990a7d0"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["- Trandum verre enn fengsel -adressa.no", "- Aldri f\u00f8lt meg s\u00e5 knust", "- Grenser for hva jeg t\u00e5ler", "S\u00e5 Stoltenberg p\u00e5 tv"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "85db9451f2d3e05ffc306deee171799e18634bbc"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "innenriks"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "law-government-and-politics"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["f\u00f8lt", "fengsel", "\u00e5pent brev", "brev"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["trandum", "gardermoen", "les maria amelies"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["jens stoltenberg", "maria amelie"]}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": ["nyheter", "nyheter/innenriks"]}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1379086.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/ameliehode169"}, {"field": "og-locale", "value": "nb_NO"}, {"field": "og-site-name", "value": "adressa.no"}, {